com.st.olm.cq.api.products

Class TransitorySTProduct

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.st.olm.cq.api.products.TransitorySTProduct
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    STProduct, org.apache.sling.api.adapter.Adaptable

    public final class TransitorySTProduct
extends Object
implements STProduct
    Represents a transitory product. This should only used to hold the data for a product from PRMIS to create the underlying node. This should not be used to represent a project for any other use.
    Author:
    dklco
